{"tid":1457354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"錯一次，唔好再錯落去","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:47:51.000Z","uid":21385,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc5f319d2c18ac7d529a775cfd0f1d912af7018e","tid":1457354,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:35:59.000Z","msg":"今日大家都見到白色恐佈嘅威力<br />\n停AEL停交通停通訊停乜乜柒柒<br />\n6點清場？自己已經清咗大半啦<br />\n<br />\n五年前我地係輸俾左膠，因為我地冇經驗<br />\n今次我地已經輸過一次，唔好輸俾散水撚<br />\n<br />\n當然可以話今日搞到機場癱瘓目標達到<br />\n係，但唔好以為咁就完成任務<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可呢啲都唔講喇<br />\n我今日出黎，就係為咗尋日個女仔<br />\n佢冇咗嘅係一生<br />\n我唔甘心佢同咁多位義士嘅犧牲<br />\n香港都係大家嘅，要攬炒就一齊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">下一次再癱瘓機場<br />\n唔好再叫人走<br />\n試下叫人支援<br />\n試下唔好驚<br />\n唔齊心就唔會成功</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"efba3b3d5d14ae446d29834438eb7915eacebad7","tid":1457354,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:36:55.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"e48eb5037fa18f70fc1b758c6b11a0924c99a80a","tid":1457354,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c00f89e8ac2e6b7729f55b72d3a68ed59c5ce9b5","tid":1457354,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:38:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62cfb275fa978852c0daea40d2ec9c1f319e7887","tid":1457354,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f46cd4c9ed98a158319f7248cdefbfe941ce108a","tid":1457354,"uid":283080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />經一事長一智！"},{"pid":"fdc6e1db4ef4d90c7998f4e2d4463abc0cbcb5ef","tid":1457354,"uid":3876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:38:50.000Z","msg":"<i